gst-launch pipeline used as sender to the regie program:
gst-launch-1.0 jackaudiosrc provide-clock=false ! audio/x-raw,channels=2 ! audiorate ! audioconvert ! taginject tags="comment=audioComment" ! vorbisenc ! matroskamux name=mux streamable=true ! gdppay ! tcpserversink host=192.168.189.220 port=5000 videotestsrc ! video/x-raw,width=640,height=360,pixel-ascpect-ratio=1/1,framerate=25/1 ! timeoverlay ! clockoverlay deltay=50 ! taginject tags="comment=videoComment" ! vp8enc threads=2 deadline=20000 ! mux.
